&lt;li&gt;Improving the efficiency or usability of existing reports and solutions by creating reusable queries or components and training junior analysts on tool basics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with product and engineering to understand technical dependencies and translate business questions into data solutions, sharing insights during cross‑functional meetings.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
