&lt;li&gt;Providing actionable insights that inform decisions and connect analysis outcomes clearly to business KPIs, suggesting optimizations based on trends or findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Breaking down analysis tasks, providing accurate estimates, and communicating expected effort and trade‑offs while factoring in data complexities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building a strong understanding of the client domain and user journeys, incorporating domain nuances into analyses and understanding dependencies with engineering, product and marketing processes.&lt;/li&gt;
